Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:23.46,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(298,0)}We sigh whenever we're about to come to a standstill
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:29.71,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}While moving on this endless journey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:37.43,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Everytime we lunge for it, it escapes and flies off.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:44.85,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}But now, there's nothing to be afraid of
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:52.78,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}The powerful ties that bind our hearts
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:58.24,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Will never come loose.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:07.96,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9}After a lifetime of searching, we finally arrived
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:13.76,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Here, where the period lies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:23.06,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}Let's change all our sorrow and rage to power.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:27.98,OP04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,298}Destiny is right within our reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:23.46,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(298,0)}終わりなき旅の途中　立ち止まりそうな時
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:29.71,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}深いため息こぼす　僕らは
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:37.43,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}掴みかけてはまた離れていった
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:44.85,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}でも今はもう何も恐れることはない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:52.78,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}心を繋ぐ強い絆は
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:58.24,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}けして解けはしないさ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:07.96,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9}探し続けて辿り着いた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:13.76,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}この場所で {\fsp8}Perio{\fsp3.2}d に
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:23.06,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}悲しみ怒り 力に変えて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:27.98,OP04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,298}運命はすぐそばに
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.12,0:00:23.46,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(298,0)}Owarinaki tabi no tochuu tachidomarisouna toki
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.46,0:00:29.71,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Fukai tameiki kobosu bokura wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.80,0:00:37.43,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Tsukamikaketewa mata hanareteitta
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.89,0:00:44.85,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Demo ima wa mou nanimo osoreru koto wa nai
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.48,0:00:52.78,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}Kokoro wo tsunagu tsuyoi kizuna wa
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.78,0:00:58.24,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Keshite hodoke wa shinai sa
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.28,0:01:07.96,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9}Sagashitsuzukete tadoritsuita
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.96,0:01:13.76,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,398}Kono basho de piriodo ni
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.92,0:01:23.06,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(398,0}Kanashimi ikari chikara ni kaete
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.06,0:01:27.98,OP04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be9\fad(0,298}Unmei wa sugu soba ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:45.21,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}The promise we never made
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:46.01,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}yet again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:50.84,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}tries to snatch our future away from us.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:56.43,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is it that we can't rejoice
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:22:57.43,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}straight from the heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.43,0:23:02.40,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}when we obtain something we've always been after?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:08.11,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,498}The overflowing tears aren't from feebleness or remorse.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:12.91,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,258)}They're fragments born from agony.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:17.95,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Of all the moments and destinies,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:26.71,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I realized there's one absolute certainty.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:29.26,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if things get tough and I'm at my limit
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:33.26,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse to give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:38.14,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, don't let go.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:45.98,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}I can feel the warmth of your right hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:49.65,ED04 Eng,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}where it's tightly joined with my left.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:45.21,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}交わしたはずのない約束が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:46.01,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}今日も
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:50.84,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}僕らの未来を奪おうとする
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:56.43,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,欲しがっていたものを手にしても
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:22:57.43,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}素直に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.43,0:23:02.40,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}うまく笑えないのはなぜだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:08.11,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,498}あふれる涙は　弱さや後悔じゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:12.91,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,258)}イタミが生んだカケラで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:17.95,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}どんな瞬間だって運命だって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:26.71,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}ひとつだけ確かなものがあると知った
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:29.26,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,限界だって困難だって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:33.26,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,あきらめたくないよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:38.14,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,このまま離さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:45.98,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}かたく握りしめた　君の右手のぬくもり
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:49.65,ED04 Kana,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}ここにあるから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.25,0:22:45.21,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Kawashita hazu no nai yakasoku ga
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:46.01,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Kyou mo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.01,0:22:50.84,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}Bokura no mirai wo ubaou to suru
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.47,0:22:56.43,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Hoshigatteita mono wo te ni shitemo
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.43,0:22:57.43,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Sunao ni
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.43,0:23:02.40,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}Umaku waraenai nowa nazedarou
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.06,0:23:08.11,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,498}Afureru namida wo yowasa ya koukai ja nai
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.78,0:23:12.91,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,258)}Itami ga unda kakera de
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.58,0:23:17.95,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Donna shunkan datte unmei datte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.95,0:23:26.71,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Hitotsu dake tashika na mono ga aru to shitta
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.71,0:23:29.26,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Genkai datte konnan datte
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.26,0:23:33.26,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Akirametakunaiyo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.26,0:23:38.14,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,Konomama hanasanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.14,0:23:45.98,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13}Kataku nigirishimeta kimi no migite no nukumori
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.98,0:23:49.65,ED04 Roma,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be13\fad(0,498)}Koko ni arukara
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.36,0:01:35.15,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,On the day before the Promised Day,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.15,0:01:38.99,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse Elric lies dormant in the Eastern training grounds.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.41,0:01:47.54,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,However, he is captured by the sudden appearances of the Homunculi, Gluttony and Pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:01:58.01,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.22,0:02:05.10,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Pick yourself up...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:06.39,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Alphonse...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.73,0:02:09.60,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Who...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.86,0:02:16.03,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,It's far too early for you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:22.49,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,I still have plenty of things for you to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.39,0:02:44.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:45.76,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Are we in Kanama?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.98,0:02:51.06,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.40,0:02:53.52,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You've got some visitors.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.49,0:03:02.49,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,So you're here, Edwa-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:06.41,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,God, that felt good.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.41,0:03:09.37,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,The first thing you do is punch me in the face?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.37,0:03:11.00,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,And with your right hand, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.84,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you made some new friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.84,0:03:15.17,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Fri-
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.17,0:03:18.17,Default,Li,0000,0000,0000,,We're just working with him due to the circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.17,0:03:20.88,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm the boss of all of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.38,0:03:24.55,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,Oh my.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.55,0:03:27.01,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for taking care of my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.01,0:03:28.18,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Not a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.18,0:03:30.56,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Though he's one hell of a brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.56,0:03:31.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:34.77,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,Interesting tattoo you've got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:36.90,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.44,0:03:38.44,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,This.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.69,0:03:41.53,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Guess there's no point in hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:45.49,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better not hide anything either, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:52.21,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow is the "Promised Day", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.21,0:03:56.21,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.92,0:03:58.88,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you guys everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.10,0:04:18.90,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,Guess you won't be able to accept it as easily as Alphonse did.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.90,0:04:20.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You told Al too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.07,0:04:22.11,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:26.91,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,He probably has a lot to think about, but he accepted it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:33.71,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,The philosopher's stone you've been looking for is right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:34.54,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to use it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:36.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't fuck with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:38.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They're lives of people who are totally uninvolved!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:41.26,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,We lost our bodies due to our own carelessness!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.26,0:04:42.42,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What gives us the right to use their lives?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.34,0:04:47.68,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad my son grew up to say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.43,0:04:54.27,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,A solar eclipse occurs tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.27,0:04:56.35,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,He's planning on using that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.65,0:04:58.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A solar eclipse?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.02,0:04:59.36,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How would he use that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.98,0:05:01.11,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,Edward.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:05.70,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,Would you be willing to help me stop his plans?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:07.49,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,'Help'?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.49,0:05:09.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Don't get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.03,0:05:13.20,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to beat the hell out of that geezer even if I {\i1}don't{\i0\fscx40} {\r} have to work with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.45,0:05:18.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just listening to what you have to say right now because teaming up with you might increase our odds of 	winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:28.43,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad to hear...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.43,0:05:32.72,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever the reason may be, you're willing to fight alongside me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.73,0:05:42.40,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Granny Pinako asked me to tell you Mom's last words.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,"Sorry I couldn't keep my promise."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:51.70,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm going to have to leave you first."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.21,0:05:59.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Message delivered!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.64,0:06:22.81,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shouldn't you try to sit knee to knee with your father and open up to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:23.98,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.98,0:06:25.90,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,You should at least call him "Old Man".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.53,0:06:28.82,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like a lot happened in the past,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.82,0:06:32.03,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,but he definitely doesn't seem like someone who would abandon his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:35.04,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,He probably has a lot of personal reasons.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.70,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Listen to what he has to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.70,0:06:39.66,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.66,0:06:41.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I've got a lot of personal reasons, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.92,0:06:43.50,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,For example?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.50,0:06:45.38,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,You're probably just too stubborn and proud.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.13,0:06:49.59,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You can't organize your thoughts very well, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.68,0:06:52.14,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Can't really blame you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.14,0:06:55.26,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He's a philosopher's stone in the shape of a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.26,0:06:58.98,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,To top it off, he's also your dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:01.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,That's not all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.77,0:07:06.98,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He just showed a side of himself that I wasn't really expecting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.58,0:07:21.62,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,You know... someday, I'll turn into a wrinkled old woman who looks like a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.58,0:07:27.63,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,But no matter how I end up looking, I'll always be happy to take a picture with the family where everyone is 	smiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:30.47,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,So please... stay with your family.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.93,0:07:34.89,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,Trisha, I'm going.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.76,0:07:37.18,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,Please wait for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.52,0:07:46.27,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.74,0:07:52.07,Default,Tri,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.08,0:08:01.91,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,"Sorry I couldn't keep my promise."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:05.33,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,"I'm going to have to leave you first.", huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.13,0:08:10.34,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,Even though we couldn't age and die together,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.92,0:08:15.68,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,you must believe from the bottom of your heart that I'll come after you in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.56,0:08:22.31,Default,Hoh,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be tomorrow... Trisha.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.48,0:08:27.98,Default,Woman,0000,0000,0000,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.98,0:08:29.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:31.53,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,What are you going to do with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.91,0:08:43.33,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to wear something flashy like this again?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:45.04,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Why's it gotta be red?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.59,0:08:53.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,This is probably going to be our last battle against them.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.38,0:08:56.18,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to need to be psyched.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.51,0:09:01.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.97,0:09:05.44,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You don't really have to stick with me through all of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.44,0:09:09.48,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I personally think it would be better for you guys if you were to leave to attend to your own business from 		here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.81,0:09:13.36,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're one of my henchmen. Don't go ordering me around.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.36,0:09:17.24,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you guys want to return to your original bodies too?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.24,0:09:18.66,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.66,0:09:23.37,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,This body can be pretty convenient.\NI guess I wouldn't mind staying like this forever.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:26.12,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That's the spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.04,0:09:28.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Then... why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.79,0:09:30.50,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.50,0:09:32.38,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,We don't really have anywhere else to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.38,0:09:37.01,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,My animal instincts tell me that I'm better off staying here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.89,0:09:41.97,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,And what about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:45.64,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you saying something about running away from the other Homunculi?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.48,0:09:49.65,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You're asking why I came back to Central?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.19,0:09:51.65,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Not tellin'.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.66,0:10:01.03,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:14.38,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.46,0:10:17.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Man, don't scare me like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:20.47,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we were able to join up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.47,0:10:21.60,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How have you been?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.60,0:10:24.22,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like you were safe and sound too, Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:27.77,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Aren't you supposed to be with Major Miles?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.18,0:10:30.02,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Is everything going well over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.44,0:10:32.27,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,I actually wanted to talk to you about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.27,0:10:33.44,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Could you come here for a second?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.44,0:10:34.82,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.86,0:10:40.28,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Al... is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.66,Default,Al,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you ask?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.66,0:10:47.95,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I dunno... I just got a feeling.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.95,0:10:49.00,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.54,0:10:50.46,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Lin!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.46,0:10:51.83,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Get away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.25,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,He's...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:57.76,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,That's...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.44,0:11:13.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.90,0:11:18.15,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,So you joined them, Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.83,0:11:29.25,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,And you were taken control of by a human like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.79,0:11:34.00,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Your soul is too weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.55,0:11:47.18,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,The Führer President is still missing?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.18,0:11:51.39,Default,Grumm,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently, all they found was the corpse of one of his men downstream.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.39,0:11:54.31,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,It would be a miracle if he were to be alive after this.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.31,0:12:00.07,Default,Grumm,0000,0000,0000,,I'll lead the search team, and I'll also ask the Northern army to lend us a hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:01.82,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,You're going to step foot on the front lines yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:07.08,Default,Grumm,0000,0000,0000,,I'll never be able to rest easy until I see his corpse with my own two eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.78,0:12:11.50,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to target Central as according to your original plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.50,0:12:13.25,Default,Grumm,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing I can do.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.25,0:12:17.59,Default,Grumm,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just have to hand over the fatty portions of Central to Colonel Mustang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.88,0:12:23.59,Default,Grumm,0000,0000,0000,,Currently, the Bradley administration is operating without any trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:30.39,Default,Grumm,0000,0000,0000,,If Colonel Mustang and Major General Armstrong were to go through with the operation,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.81,Default,Grumm,0000,0000,0000,,they'll probably be treated as rebels.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:36.60,Default,Grumm,0000,0000,0000,,And when that happens, it'll be my turn to shine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.69,0:12:40.44,Default,Grumm,0000,0000,0000,,After they become seen as the villains,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.44,0:12:45.11,Default,Grumm,0000,0000,0000,,I, Lieutenant General Grumman, the defender of justice, will arrive on the scene.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:50.58,Default,Grumm,0000,0000,0000,,In order for me to stand at the top of this country with the least amount of risk,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.58,0:12:54.50,Default,Grumm,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to need the younglings to pull the chestnuts out of the fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.37,0:12:59.63,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,That's probably exactly what this raccoon is thinking right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.80,0:13:05.26,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,I joined forces with him since we're right on the brink of the Promised Day,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:08.55,Default,Miles,0000,0000,0000,,but I shouldn't let my guard down until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:20.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A-Al...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.90,0:13:21.98,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,It's Pride.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.82,0:13:24.11,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,'Pride'?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.11,0:13:25.70,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.70,0:13:29.49,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I guess he's sort of like our eldest brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.53,0:13:31.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,A Homunculus?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:37.33,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,So you're going to betray us no matter what, Greed?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:42.25,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Then at this point, you're nothing but an obstacle for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.25,0:13:43.63,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Damn you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.63,0:13:45.34,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,How did you know we were here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.13,0:13:50.51,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you transform into Al!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.51,0:13:52.60,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't transform into anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.02,0:13:58.14,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,This is really your little brother's body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:04.78,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You son of a...!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.53,0:14:08.82,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to dispose of Greed right here and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.82,0:14:12.45,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,And then, I'm going to have the Fullmetal Alchemist come with me afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.04,0:14:17.41,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! You two should hide somewhere-
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.41,0:14:19.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, you guys sure didn't waste any time, did you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:23.29,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Our animal instincts are telling us not to fight that thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.92,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to be okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.38,0:14:29.13,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.13,0:14:31.85,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,They can't kill Al and I because they need us for whatever reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.22,0:14:35.27,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,But on the other hand, I can give them everything I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.27,0:14:37.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to beat you to a pulp!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:40.81,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,You're right; I'm not going to kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.35,0:14:45.40,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,However, I can't guarantee that you won't lose a limb or three.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.78,0:14:55.29,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I can't escape into the slums!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:05.59,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You can't guard against this guy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.34,0:15:08.55,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That was close!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.47,0:15:17.22,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I've captured your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:22.77,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Do I also have to capture the people in the slums in order for you to cooperate with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.02,0:15:25.69,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.69,0:15:28.86,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He's going right for your soft spots.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:46.50,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I can't be on the losing side all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.90,0:16:06.77,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:07.44,Default,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,A power outage?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.44,0:16:08.82,Default,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.99,0:16:18.08,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I can't see anything,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.08,0:16:19.62,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,but the eyeballs have also disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.54,0:16:23.62,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Greed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.62,0:16:24.75,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Heinekel?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.12,0:16:26.13,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:27.50,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.50,0:16:30.55,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,A shadow only exists if there is light.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.55,0:16:33.01,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He can't even materialize in the dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.01,0:16:35.68,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,and can't see anything just like us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.18,0:16:37.68,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,So he left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:39.81,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He's just lurking somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.81,0:16:42.39,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,If the lights come back on, he'll be back...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:44.73,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,What are we going to do, then?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.77,0:16:49.19,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Heinekel... did you see Alphonse's shadow earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.19,0:16:50.19,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.19,0:16:52.53,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,There were a lot of these tentacles crawling about.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.53,0:16:53.57,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Not that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:56.78,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He was always near a large shadow, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:17:00.33,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Pride's real body is somewhere within the shadows of the forest.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.74,0:17:01.79,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,His real body?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:04.41,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,So it's not in Al's armor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.41,0:17:05.96,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.96,0:17:09.67,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He has a container just for himself to use whenever he goes out.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:11.96,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of 'container'?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:21.81,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,No moon or stars in the sky, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.85,0:17:26.23,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,They can't maneuver in this darkness either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.94,0:17:29.44,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I'll just have to wait for the slums to get their power back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.11,0:17:37.45,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,You're not getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.32,0:17:43.66,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,So my child's figure doesn't stop you from attacking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.66,0:17:44.91,Default,Pride,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.91,0:17:48.54,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,You're right. I do feel bad for having to kill a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.21,0:17:52.05,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,But then again,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:54.42,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,my animal instincts are overwhelming my conscience!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.84,0:17:58.01,Default,Hei,0000,0000,0000,,It's telling me that I have to kill you here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.26,0:18:03.01,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.10,0:18:04.93,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ed!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.56,0:18:06.52,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Is that you, Donkey Kong?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.64,0:18:09.06,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,How's your little brother doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.06,0:18:10.94,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,He doesn't seem to have moved at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.94,0:18:13.19,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You can hear it when he does.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.69,0:18:16.32,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Let's leave this place for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.32,0:18:17.90,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,You're telling me to abandon Al?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.24,0:18:20.57,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,I understand that you're worried,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.57,0:18:22.91,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,but what if we were to approach him carelessly, just to find that it was a 	trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.87,0:18:29.62,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,We need to stick together until Heinekel takes care of Pride in order to avoid accidentally attacking each 	other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.25,0:18:36.92,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Is that... the sound of Lion King fighting?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:41.39,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Let's just leave it to the nocturnals for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.56,0:18:46.06,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Damn that Pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:48.77,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,How did he know we were here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.77,0:18:51.02,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That shouldn't be a part of his abilities...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:57.28,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Duck!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.62,0:19:12.88,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Smells like the Fullmetal Alchemist.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.88,0:19:14.79,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Smells like Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:17.00,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Judging from the voice... Gluttony?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.00,0:19:18.17,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.17,0:19:19.72,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Now I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.72,0:19:24.05,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He used Gluttony's keen sense of smell to find us.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.47,0:19:29.68,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I also smell a scent of a guy I don't recognize!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.68,0:19:31.60,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I can eat him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.02,0:19:34.31,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He's talking about you, Darius.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.31,0:19:36.40,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That one's also a Homunculus.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.40,0:19:38.61,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,How do you expect me to fight against a monster like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.24,0:19:42.49,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,He's just following his nose.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.49,0:19:46.70,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,In this situation, you should be evenly matched.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.70,0:19:50.50,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,My animal instincts are telling me not to do it, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.96,0:19:54.08,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Men are all about guts!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.75,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Victory goes to the swiftest!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.18,0:20:05.89,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,One more!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.93,0:20:10.14,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, Donkey Kong...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.14,0:20:13.98,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I thought we were sticking together to avoid attacking each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:14.69,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.31,0:20:19.32,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Gluttony will still have the advantage in the dark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.32,0:20:21.94,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,But if we were to turn on the lights, Pride would...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.95,0:20:24.70,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,This is troublesome.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.36,0:20:26.70,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Greed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.20,0:20:27.99,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,That you, Lin?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.66,0:20:29.83,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Switch with me for a sec.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:33.92,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I can sense the aura of the Homunculi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:36.08,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I was also the one to notice Pride, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:39.71,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I can fight better than you in this darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.13,0:20:44.26,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Guess I don't have a choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.26,0:20:46.76,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,You better not run off with this body!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:47.76,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the jokes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.76,0:20:49.06,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,It's my body to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:51.72,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,Rub a dub dub, thanks for the-
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.72,0:20:52.93,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:20:59.65,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,Nice one!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.65,0:21:01.53,Default,Greed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I picked you, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.53,0:21:02.03,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm honored!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.65,0:21:03.61,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Is it Lin now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.61,0:21:03.99,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.86,0:21:06.78,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,You're making me angry...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:08.28,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm also hungry!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.28,0:21:11.24,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,But you guys aren't letting me eat you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.70,0:21:12.95,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.95,0:21:16.00,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,...I'm just going to swallow you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.29,0:21:17.63,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,I have a bad feeling!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.63,0:21:18.75,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.00,0:21:20.21,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Something's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.21,0:21:21.63,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What{\i0\fscx40} {\r}, exactly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.96,0:21:24.01,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,This is... just like back then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.01,0:21:24.88,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... Whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.88,0:21:27.01,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What do you guys see that I don't?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.01,0:21:29.39,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a normal guy! Explain it to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.69,0:21:41.57,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.15,0:21:43.07,Default,Dar,0000,0000,0000,,Stay still!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.07,0:21:47.99,Default,Ed,0000,0000,0000,,Is there someone else?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.99,0:21:48.66,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.41,0:21:51.91,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't got a clue, but this is...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.62,0:21:54.79,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:21:59.83,Default,Glut,0000,0000,0000,,I know this smell...!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.44,0:22:20.98,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,Glad to see you're in top shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.02,0:22:24.57,Default,Lin,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for you, Lan Fan!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.41,0:24:02.58,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,If you only feel fear after knowing both the abilities of your enemy and yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.58,0:24:04.75,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,flee with your tail between your legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.25,0:24:08.84,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,However, if you're going to stand firm and fight with a focused mind,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.84,0:24:11.09,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,you will definitely have victory within reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.17,0:24:16.39,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Next time, Fullmetal Alchemist:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.39,0:24:20.39,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 48, The Oath in the Tunnel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.98,0:24:25.40,Default,Nar,0000,0000,0000,,Is it right or wrong to achieve victory by sacrificing a fellow comrade?
